::SnowCat::

She walked around and found roughly where the brig of the Ark would 
be.  She sniffed around and smelled the scent of Predacons.  She 
growled in her snow leopard mode.  She didn't liek that scent at 
all.  It was the same scent she had encounteredin the forest untill 
the Maximals arrived to help her.  She continued scouting around and 
becoming familiar with her surroundings.
